<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Phone rings.  Unknown number.  </em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
Me: &quot;Hello&quot;<br>
<br>
Them: &quot;Hello.  Is John in?&quot;<br>
<br>
Me: &quot;Who is calling please?&quot;<br>
<br>
Them: &quot;Who is this?  Are you his wife?&quot;<br>
<br>
Me: &quot;None of your business, you're calling me.  I'll try this again.  Who is this?&quot;<br>
<br>
Them: &quot;This is Joe.  Who are you?&quot;<br>
<br>
Me: &quot;I said, none of your business and we don't know any Joe's.  What do you want?&quot;<br>
<br>
Them: &quot;Who are you?  Are you his spouse?&quot;<br>
<br>
Me: &quot;What do you want? Unless you tell me what you are calling us about I'm hanging up this phone, now.&quot;<br>
<br>
Them: &quot;This is a banking matter&quot;.  <br>
<br>
Me: &quot;There now, that wasn't too hard now was it?  He's at work.&quot;<br>
<br>
Them: &quot;Is this his spouse?&quot;<br>
<br>
Me: &quot;No&quot;<br>
<br>
